front.title: •Captain Jonus in Scimitar 2
front.gametext: Permanent pilot is *Jonus, who provides ability of 2. This starship's missile weapon destiny draws are +1. If at a system you control, your total power at related sites is +1.
front.lore: TIE bomber repaired after being struck by an asteroid in the Anoat system. Stationed aboard second Death Star battle station.
